text: Morforex (INN; Bo 637), also referable to as N-morpholinoethylamphetamine, is an anorectic which was never marketed. It produces amphetamine as an active metabolite. ==See also== * Fenethylline * Phenmetrazine ==References== Category:Substituted amphetamines Category:Anorectics Category:Morpholines Category:Norepinephrine-dopamine releasing agents
title: Morforex
